Package edu.monash.fit2099.game.grounds

This module is about the grounds within the edu.monash.fit2099.game.

This module explores the different grounds that can exist on the map. Each ground has different functionality and way of being dealt by actors, and some grounds are related to each other (ie: Tree and its subclasses). Note that all grounds in this package extend the abstract ground class in engine package.

Since:
1.0.0
